member.summary:
Whitelist of content sources. By default allow all content from the current site and specific domains for different types of content.


    default-src 'self' (Default source for all content groups. Fallback for any resource group that has not been specified.)



    script-src 'self' (allow all scripts from current domain) maps.googleapis.com (Google maps for address field) *.gstatic.com (backend login), www.google.com, apis.google.com, *.google-analytics.com (analytics), connect.facebook.net (social share) ajax.aspnetcdn.com (mvc, scheduling etc.); https://www.youtube.com platform.twitter.com https://syndication.twitter.com/ https://s.ytimg.com https://publish.twitter.com *.twimg.com (embed tweets and youtube links) platform.linkedin.com http://platform.stumbleupon.com/1/widgets.js (social share) https://*.googletagmanager.com (Google tag manager); 



    style-src 'self' (allow all styles from current domain) fonts.googleapis.com (backend login) netdna.bootstrapcdn.com kendo.cdn.telerik.com www.google.com (Angular backend) platform.twitter.com/css/ *.twimg.com (embed tweets);



    img-src 'self' (allow all images from current domain) maps.gstatic.com maps.googleapis.com (Google maps for address field), platform.tumblr.com web.facebook.com www.facebook.com www.redditstatic.com www.linkedin.com https://syndication.twitter.com https://static.licdn.com/scds/common/u/images/apps/connect/sprites/sprite_connect_v14.png (social share), pbs.twimg.com platform.twitter.com/css *.twimg.com (twitter images), data: (allows loading images via data scheme - Base64 encoded), blob: (allows images from local file system), i.ytimg.com  (Embedding content from Youtube) https://*.googletagmanager.com (Google tag manager);



    font-src 'self' (allow all fonts from current domain) fonts.gstatic.com kendo.cdn.telerik.com netdna.bootstrapcdn.com data: (backend login, angular backend); 



    frame-src 'self' (allow all frames from current domain) 



    connect-src 'self' (allow all XHR, WebSocket, EventSource calls from/to the current domain) data: (allows the preview of GoogleAmp) accounts.google.com (social share) *.google-analytics.com (analytics) https://*.insight.sitefinity.com (Insight) https://*.dec.sitefinity.com (legacy DEC) *.mktoresp.com (Marketo) https://*.googletagmanager.com (Google tag manager)



    media-src 'self' (allow all media from current domain) data: (Angular backend) blob: (allow media from local file system)



    child-src 'self' apis.google.com accounts.google.com staticxx.facebook.com www.facebook.com web.facebook.com badge.stumbleupon.com (social share) https://platform.twitter.com/ https://syndication.twitter.com/ https://www.youtube.com/ youtube-nocookie.com https://player.vimeo.com/ https://w.soundcloud.com/ (embed tweets and video and music sites links) web-chat.nativechat.com (NativeChat connector)
